task.summary: Print (relative path) of all files in directory/subdirectory
Print relative path and last time modified of all files in directory/subdirectory

Send files to pi
Instructions:
1) In root directory, run "sbt assembly" 2) Move jar wherever you want 3) run "scala jar-name arg0 arg1"
Arg0 = Local file name (relative to current directory, Ex. "a.docx") Arg1 = Pi's IP address
